body:
Yes, IIRC there was a problem compiling the SVD op, so it was originally excluded from the (CMake) build. I can look into it later, or you could try commenting out [this line](https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/7f3d8e1f8736f4c812e4a0a96154af3bd3750180/tensorflow/contrib/cmake/tf_core_kernels.cmake#L93) in this CL and running the tests again....

[The unrelated `reader_ops_test.py` failure is being caused by an old version of SWIG on the Jenkins machines, and there's a fix for that in the pipeline.]
